---
const title = "Casa de la Grana · Centro cultural";
const description = "Centro cultural dedicado a la preservación de la grana cochinilla y su significado histórico. Naturaleza, historia y cultura en Oaxaca.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
  <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/images/img-05.jpg" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/isotipo-rojo.svg" />
  <style>
    /* ---- FONTS ---- */
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Chivo';
      src: url('/fonts/Chivo-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Chivo';
      src: url('/fonts/Chivo-Italic-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'ChivoMono';
      src: url('/fonts/ChivoMono-VariableFont_wght.ttf') format('truetype');
      font-weight: 100 900;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Koper';
      src: url('/fonts/Koper-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    /* ---- TOKENS ---- */
    :root {
      --negro:      #231C1A;
      --crema:      #F7F3F0;
      --grana:      #A31300;
      --nduku:      #66123C;
      --buganvilia: #E2ACC5;
      --achiote:    #D87239;
      --font-mono:  'ChivoMono', monospace;
      --font-sans:  'Chivo', sans-serif;
      --font-serif: 'Koper', serif;
    }

    /* ---- RESET ---- */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      background: var(--crema);
      color: var(--negro);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ---- NAV TOP ---- */
    .nav-top {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      /* transparent by default, crema on scroll */
      background: transparent;
      transition: background 0.4s, border-color 0.4s;
    }
    .nav-top.scrolled {
      background: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.07);
    }
    .nav-logo-link img {
      height: 20px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
      /* white logo on dark hero, auto-switch */
      filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
      transition: filter 0.4s;
    }
    .nav-top.scrolled .nav-logo-link img {
      filter: none;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.65);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-top.scrolled .nav-links a { color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.55); }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--crema); }
    .nav-top.scrolled .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--negro); }

    /* ---- HERO ---- */
    .hero {
      background: var(--negro);
      min-height: 100svh;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 180px 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 6rem 2.5rem 4rem;
    }
    .hero-word-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-self: flex-start;
      padding-top: 8vh;
    }
    .hero-word-right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-end;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: right;
      align-self: flex-end;
      padding-bottom: 8vh;
    }
    .hero-huge {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: 200;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6.5vw, 6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--crema);
      line-height: 0.92;
      display: block;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.35);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .hero-circles {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }
    .hero-circle {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.1);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .hero-circle img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
    }
    .hero-footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2rem;
      left: 0; right: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.22);
    }

    /* ---- TICKER ---- */
    .ticker {
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--grana);
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .ticker-track {
      display: inline-flex;
      animation: ticker 32s linear infinite;
    }
    .ticker-track span {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--crema);
      padding-right: 3rem;
    }
    .ticker-track .sep {
      color: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.35);
      padding-right: 3rem;
    }
    @keyframes ticker {
      0%   { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ---- MANIFESTO ---- */
    .manifesto {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .manifesto-text {
      padding: 7rem 4rem 7rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--grana);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .manifesto-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--negro);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      font-style: normal;
    }
    .manifesto-heading em {
      color: var(--grana);
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .manifesto-body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.82);
      max-width: 44ch;
    }
    .manifesto-body p + p { margin-top: 1em; }
    .manifesto-img {
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 540px;
    }
    .manifesto-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.8s ease;
    }
    .manifesto-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

    /* ---- QUOTE ---- */
    .quote-block {
      background: var(--negro);
      padding: 8rem 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .quote-text {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--buganvilia);
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .quote-attr {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(226, 172, 197, 0.35);
      font-style: normal;
    }

    /* ---- SUAJE / PARALLAX ---- */
    .suaje-section {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--crema);
      min-height: 85vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .suaje-blob {
      position: absolute;
      left: -8%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 55vw;
      max-width: 720px;
      pointer-events: none;
      will-change: transform;
    }
    .suaje-blob img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .suaje-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-left: auto;
      padding: 6rem 2.5rem 6rem 0;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    .suaje-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--negro);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .suaje-sub {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.45);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: 1px solid currentColor;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-negro {
      color: var(--negro);
      border-color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-negro:hover { background: var(--negro); color: var(--crema); }
    .btn-grana { background: var(--grana); color: var(--crema); border-color: var(--grana); }
    .btn-grana:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--grana); }
    .btn-light { color: rgba(247,243,240,0.65); border-color: rgba(247,243,240,0.25); }
    .btn-light:hover { background: var(--crema); color: var(--negro); border-color: var(--crema); }

    /* ---- GALLERY ---- */
    .gallery-section {
      padding: 5rem 2.5rem 4rem;
      background: var(--crema);
    }
    .gallery-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .gallery-title {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--negro);
    }
    .gallery-count {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.3);
    }
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.05);
    }
    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .gallery-item.tall { grid-row: span 2; }
    .gallery-item.wide { grid-column: span 2; }

    .products-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0.35rem;
      margin-top: 0.35rem;
    }
    .product-item {
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.03);
    }
    .product-item img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .product-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }

    /* ---- BRIDGE ---- */
    .bridge {
      background: var(--negro);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .bridge-text {
      padding: 7rem 4rem 7rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .bridge .section-label { color: var(--achiote); }
    .bridge-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: 200;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--crema);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.0;
    }
    .bridge-body {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.5);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 44ch;
    }
    .bridge-links { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .bridge-img {
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 500px;
    }
    .bridge-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
    footer {
      background: var(--crema);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.08);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .footer-contact address {
      font-style: normal;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      line-height: 2.1;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.55);
    }
    .footer-contact a:hover { color: var(--grana); }
    .footer-logo-wrap { text-align: center; }
    .footer-logo-wrap img { height: 26px; width: auto; margin: 0 auto; }
    .footer-sub {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.28);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-copy {
      text-align: right;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.28);
    }

    /* ---- FLOATING NAV ---- */
    .floating-nav {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 98;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(247, 243, 240, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.1);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.1);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .floating-nav a {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.6);
      padding: 0.65rem 1.1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      display: block;
    }
    .floating-nav a:hover { color: var(--negro); }
    .floating-nav a + a {
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(35, 28, 26, 0.08);
    }
    .floating-nav a:first-child { border-radius: 100px 0 0 100px; }
    .floating-nav a:last-child  { border-radius: 0 100px 100px 0; }

    /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .nav-top { padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .floating-nav { display: none; }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 5rem 1.25rem 3rem;
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }
      .hero-word-left { align-self: auto; padding-top: 0; }
      .hero-word-right { align-items: flex-start; text-align: left; align-self: auto; padding-bottom: 0; }
      .hero-circles {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        order: -1;
      }
      .hero-circle { width: 90px; height: 90px; }

      .manifesto { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .manifesto-text { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
      .manifesto-img { min-height: 280px; order: -1; }

      .suaje-section { min-height: auto; }
      .suaje-blob { display: none; }
      .suaje-content { margin: 0; padding: 4rem 1.25rem; max-width: 100%; }

      .gallery-section { padding: 4rem 1.25rem 3rem; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .products-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }

      .bridge { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .bridge-text { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
      .bridge-img { min-height: 260px; }

      footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
      .footer-copy { text-align: center; }
      .footer-contact address { text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- NAV TOP -->
  <nav class="nav-top" id="nav-top">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo-link" aria-label="Casa de la Grana">
      <img src="/images/logo-negro.svg" alt="Casa de la Grana" />
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/nocheztlicalli/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://nocheztlicalli.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nocheztlicalli</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">

      <div class="hero-word-left">
        <span class="hero-huge">Descubre</span>
        <p class="hero-tag">Naturaleza<br/>Historia<br/>Cultura</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-circles">
        <div class="hero-circle">
          <img src="/images/img-06.jpg" alt="Grana cochinilla" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <div class="hero-circle">
          <img src="/images/img-09.jpg" alt="Tintes naturales" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <div class="hero-circle">
          <img src="/images/img-10.jpg" alt="Arte oaxaqueño" loading="eager" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-word-right">
        <p class="hero-tag">Tradición<br/>Arte<br/>Preservación</p>
        <span class="hero-huge">El Secreto</span>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="hero-footer">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Centro Cultural &middot; Casa de la Grana &middot; Oaxaca</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TICKER -->
  <div class="ticker" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="ticker-track">
      <span>Tradición</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Arte</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Grana Cochinilla</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Oaxaca</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Nocheztlicalli</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Tintes Naturales</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Preservación</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Patrimonio</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Tradición</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Arte</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Grana Cochinilla</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Oaxaca</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Nocheztlicalli</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Tintes Naturales</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Preservación</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>Patrimonio</span><span class="sep">&middot;</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MANIFESTO -->
  <section class="manifesto">
    <div class="manifesto-text">
      <p class="section-label">01 &mdash; Nuestro pasado en la actualidad</p>
      <h2 class="manifesto-heading">La grana que<br/>colorea nuestra<br/><em>historia</em></h2>
      <div class="manifesto-body">
        <p>Casa de la Grana preserva la práctica tradicional del cultivo de la grana cochinilla y comparte su significado histórico. Un espacio donde el conocimiento científico se entrelaza con la experiencia creativa.</p>
        <p>Desde Oaxaca, rescatamos el legado de Nocheztlicalli - el insecto sagrado que tiñó imperios y continúa siendo fuente de vida y arte para nuestra comunidad.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="manifesto-img">
      <img src="/images/img-11.jpg" alt="Nopal con cochinilla" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUOTE -->
  <section class="quote-block">
    <blockquote>
      <p class="quote-text">"nuestras raíces no solo nos definen, sino que la naturaleza nos ofrece enseñanzas"</p>
      <cite class="quote-attr">Nocheztlicalli &middot; Casa de la Grana</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- SUAJE / PARALLAX -->
  <section class="suaje-section" id="suaje-section">
    <div class="suaje-blob" id="suaje-blob" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/images/isotipo-rojo.svg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="suaje-content">
      <p class="section-label">02 &mdash; El color del legado</p>
      <h2 class="suaje-heading">Descubre el color<br/>del legado<br/>mexicano</h2>
      <p class="suaje-sub">Junto a las guardianas del legado oaxaqueño</p>
      <a href="https://nocheztlicalli.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-negro">Visítanos</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GALLERY -->
  <section class="gallery-section">
    <div class="gallery-header">
      <h2 class="gallery-title">Galería</h2>
      <span class="gallery-count">Proyecto CEDIM &middot; 2024</span>
